casebody.data:
In re West.

[Cite as In re West (2001), 92 Ohio St.3d 82.]

(No. 00-1607 Submitted May 30, 2001 Decided June 20, 2001.) David H. Bodiker, State Public Defender, and Felice Harris, Assistant State Public Defender, for appellant.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of In re Anderson (2001), 92 Ohio St.3d 63, 748 N.E.2d 67.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Cook, J., dissents.
